                                  DXL is the largest one-stop-shop for men's big and tall clothing, shoes in extended sizes, accessories, and home & living products for a plus-sized lifestyle.  Shop big and tall shirts, dress pants, jeans, and outerwear with thousands of styles to choose from. Most popular Big & Tall brands in a variety of styles and sizes, including Polo Ralph Lauren®, Calvin Klein®, and Tommy Bahama®, as well as private label brands like Canyon Ridge, Oak Hill, Harbor Bay and 555 Turnpike. Sizes available - Waists: 38-66; Big Sizes: XL-7XL; Tall Sizes: XLT-7XLT; Shoe Sizes: 10-18, widths to 6E.   












